/td><td>Escarlata Sal</td></tr><tr><td>13</td><td>Adro Venniser</td><td>43</td><td>Pete el Apestoso</td></tr><tr><td>14</td><td>Penitente Sombrío</td><td>44</td><td>Shayra Ventassen</td></tr><tr><td>15</td><td>Jim Queso</td><td>45</td><td>Drax el Acuchillador</td></tr><tr><td>16</td><td>Sutton Vries</td><td>46</td><td>La pequeña Cleo</td></tr><tr><td>21</td><td>Hali la Cuenstista</td><td>51</td><td>Streph el Titubeante</td></tr><tr><td>22</td><td>William Magnus</td><td>52</td><td>Brimmer Manoclonada</td></tr><tr><td>23</td><td>Abra Harper</td><td>53</td><td>Ópalo Bivaciado</td></tr><tr><td>24</td><td>Scarr</td><td>54</td><td>Targ Matagatos</td></tr><tr><td>25</td><td>Ben Parr</td><td>55</td><td>Florian el Gordo</td></tr><tr><td>26</td><td>Halcón Kolx</td><td>56</td><td>Cerdic</td></tr><tr><td>31</td><td>Maestro Dank</td><td>61</td><td>Viejo Jaek</td></tr><tr><td>32</td><td>Golim Gryer</td><td>62</td><td>Laerte</td></tr><tr><td>33</td><td>Edd Ley</td><td>63</td><td>Ramsay Grog</td></tr><tr><td>34</td><td>Kagni Vasiir</td><td>64</td><td>Sperric</td></tr><tr><td>35</td><td>Silencioso Unter</td><td>65</td><td>Belit la Segadora</td></tr><tr><td>36</td><td>Wulf Hachasangrienta</td><td>66</td><td>Ed Tech</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Rarezas de los tripulantes</h3><table><tbody><tr><td style=\"width:2em\">11</td><td style=\"width:20em\">Pierna cibernética</td><td style=\"width:2em\">41</td><td>Sediento de sangre</td></tr><tr><td>12</td><td>Alcohólico</td><td>42</td><td>Se marea en el espacio</td></tr><tr><td>13</td><td>Sed de venganza</td><td>43</td><td>Siempre nervioso</td></tr><tr><td>14</td><td>Siempre lleva un cuchillo</td><td>44</td><td>Cuenta largas historias sobre los buenos tiempos</td></tr><tr><td>15</td><td>Pelo o barba multicolor</td><td>45</td><td>Con cicatrices horribles</td></tr><tr><td>16</td><td>Una vez disparó a un hombre en el Distrito 268 solo para verlo morir</td><td>46</td><td>Parche</td></tr><tr><td>21</td><td>Cree que tiene poderes psiónicos</td><td>5